IWC data

Tidying IWC data relevant for Southern Hemisphere catch from pelagic, land based and Soviet Union corrected numbers

SHL.CSV & SHL.TXT Individual data and Header records for catches from the Antarctic land-stations SHP1.CSV & SHP1.TXT Part 1 of Individual data and Header records for pelagic catches in the Antarctic SHP2.CSV & SHP2.TXT Part 2 of Individual data and Header records for pelagic catches in the Antarctic SU.CSV and SU.TXT Revised Individual data and Header records for catches in the Antarctic taken by the Soviet Union

Load required libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)

Whale species coding for variable Sp

Species.code<-c(1:22)

##function to convert ft and inches to cm
ft.in.2cm<-function(x){
    return(((as.numeric(substring(as.character(x), 1, 2))*12)+as.numeric(substring(as.character(x), 3, 4)))*2.54)
}

ft2cm<-function(x){
    return((as.numeric(substring(as.character(x), 1, 2))*12)*2.54)
}
